LogFile.FinalText: Incredible as they are alike. This is what many think about our two princesses. Mary and Marie share many similarities, but also just as many if not more differences. They both come from abroad, they are born citizens and both also found each their prince of Denmark: Mary is married to Crown Prince Frederik, and Mary to Prince Joachim. Also their names and looks are very similar. They are both beautiful as models with long, dark hair and large brown eyes. In spite of the many simarities, however, Mary and Marie are also two independent individuals who have lived and live each in their way, and who have their own special values and character.
